            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Hosea.1:1-3:5",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EHosea%201%3A1-3%3A5%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22hose_1_1%22%20bk%3D%22hose%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EHosea%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20gave%20this%20message%20to%20Hosea%20son%20of%20Beeri%20during%20the%20years%20when%20Uzziah%2C%20Jotham%2C%20Ahaz%2C%20and%20Hezekiah%20were%20kings%20of%20Judah%2C%20and%20Jeroboam%20son%20of%20Jehoash%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E1%3A1%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EJoash%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20variant%20spelling%20of%20Jehoash.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20was%20king%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22hose_1_2%22%20bk%3D%22hose%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EHosea%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Wife%20and%20Children%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20first%20began%20speaking%20to%20Israel%20through%20Hosea%2C%20he%20said%20to%20him%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BGo%20and%20marry%20a%20prostitute%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E1%3A2%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Ea%20promiscuous%20woman.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20so%20that%20some%20of%20her%20children%20will%20be%20conceived%20in%20prostitution.%20This%20will%20illustrate%20how%20Israel%20has%20acted%20like%20a%20prostitute%20by%20turning%20against%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20worshiping%20other%20gods.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22hose_1_3%22%20bk%3D%22hose%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Hosea%20married%20Gomer%2C%20the%20daughter%20of%20Diblaim%2C%20and%20she%20became%20pregnant%20and%20gave%20Hosea%20a%20son.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22hose_1_4%22%20bk%3D%22hose%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BName%20the%20child%20Jezreel%2C%20for%20I%20am%20about%20to%20punish%20King%20Jehu%26%23x2019%3Bs%20dynasty%20to%20avenge%20the%20murders%20he%20committed%20at%20Jezreel.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20will%20bring%20an%20end%20to%20Israel%26%23x2019%3Bs%20independence.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22hose_1_5%22%20bk%3D%22hose%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20will%20break%20its%20military%20power%20in%20the%20Jezreel%20Valley.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22hose_1_6%22%20bk%3D%22hose%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3ESoon%20Gomer%20became%20pregnant%20again%20and%20gave%20birth%20to%20a%20daughter.%20And%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20said%20to%20Hosea%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BName%20your%20daughter%20Lo-ruhamah%26%23x2014%3B%26%23x2018%3BNot%20loved%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x2014%3Bfor%20I%20will%20no%20longer%20show%20love%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20or%20forgive%20them.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22hose_1_7%22%20bk%3D%22hose%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20I%20will%20show%20love%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Judah.%20I%20will%20free%20them%20from%20their%20enemies%26%23x2014%3Bnot%20with%20weapons%20and%20armies%20or%20horses%20and%20charioteers%2C%20but%20by%20my%20power%20as%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20their%20God.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22hose_1_8%22%20bk%3D%22hose%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EAfter%20Gomer%20had%20weaned%20Lo-ruhamah%2C%20she%20again%20became%20pregnant%20and%20gave%20birth%20to%20a%20second%20son.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22hose_1_9%22%20bk%3D%22hose%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BName%20him%20Lo-ammi%26%23x2014%3B%26%23x2018%3BNot%20my%20people%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x2014%3Bfor%20Israel%20is%20not%20my%20people%2C%20and%20I%20am%20not%20their%20God.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22hose_1_10%22%20bk%3D%22hose%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E1%3A10%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Verses%201%3A10-11%20are%20numbered%202%3A1-2%20in%20Hebrew%20text.%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BYet%20the%20time%20will%20come%20when%20Israel%26%23x2019%3Bs%20people%20will%20be%20like%20the%20sands%20of%20the%20seashore%26%23x2014%3Btoo%20many%20to%20count!%20Then%2C%20at%20the%20place%20where%20they%20were%20told%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BYou%20are%20not%20my%20people%2C%26%23x2019%3B%20it%20will%20be%20said%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BYou%20are%20children%20of%20the%20living%20God.%26%23x2019%3B%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22hose_1_11%22%20bk%3D%22hose%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20people%20of%20Judah%20and%20Israel%20will%20unite%20together.%20They%20will%20choose%20one%20leader%20for%20themselves%2C%20and%20they%20will%20return%20from%20exile%20t